drumkit_info.name: Roland_MC-307_TR-909
drumkit_info.author: wolke
drumkit_info.info:
This TR-909 drum-set is a original copy fom an mc-307 groovebox. The instrument order in this h2 drum-kit are arranged in the same order as they are on the goovebox.

This set contains 64 Instruments. Each instrument is recorded in 6 layers.

happy drumming
